{"tid":797350,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"同omate已經識左一年 到底應唔應該同佢表白","createTime":"2018-08-28T12:31:09.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-28T12:59:29.000Z","uid":33783,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"a5ce03d886871973e07e253e8ba45c2048153e9f","tid":797350,"uid":33783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T12:31:09.000Z","msg":"第一次相遇係響ocamp到識<br />\n佢笑起上黎好可愛又講野又斯文<br />\n打扮又樸素唔會好似一般女仔咁盲目跟韓風<br />\n果時大家都仲係freshmen傻下傻下咁<br />\n玩下game吹下水好自然就玩埋一齊<br />\n<br />\n最記得有一次佢約我出黎<br />\n果次係我第一次單獨同佢出街<br />\n但原來係想我幫佢揀生日禮物比男朋友<br />\n我到果刻先知原來原來佢已經拍左一年拖<br />\n果刻真係好心痛好想搵窿捐<br />\n但我成程強顏歡笑忍到番屋企喊左一餐<br />\n之後我都冇再主動approach佢<br />\n就連whatapps都冇再講野<br />\n<br />\n直到一個月有朋友同我講話佢ig story佢講同條囝散左<br />\n我好想主動搵佢出黎食飯但一直都唔敢<br />\n但當我諗翻起大家以前hehe哈哈一齊行街睇戲食飯同埋做gym既日子既時候<br />\n我個心就會up住up住<br />\n到底me應該點算&hellip;&hellip;"},{"pid":"cc25c0a3cc10b086a0906d8d85cde50f5f9eba0a","tid":797350,"uid":12421,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T12:45:38.000Z","msg":"重諗緊咩叫オマテ<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4898c86f5990b54bffd62939a8b7d773fe92db5c","tid":797350,"uid":14797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cc25c0a3cc10b086a0906d8d85cde50f5f9eba0a","tid":797350,"uid":12421,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T12:45:38.000Z","msg":"重諗緊咩叫オマテ<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T12:46:35.000Z","msg":"#metoo<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41d7b6cda0474be20a419e87f9a95d1ec8dbc0ec","tid":797350,"uid":150609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T12:47:28.000Z","msg":"aecom請唔請2仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7ebb90291bc265aa00c2d6c05a533742180e52a","tid":797350,"uid":76364